The paper deals with the synthesis of distributed strategies in infinite games with imperfect information, which involves topics such as logic, game theory, distributed computing, artificial intelligence, and control systems. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science), followed by cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory), cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.SY (Systems and Control).
